About Monograph

What?

Welcome to Monograph, a personal design blog dedicated to exploring the fascinating world of design. Started as a passion project. Now something with a bit more meaning.

Monograph aims to inspire, inform, and start a conversation. We jump into the creative process, exchanging thoughts and perspectives, and celebrate the beauty of design together.

Who?

Monograph was created by Kate. A passionate designer who loves all things creative. She has worked for and with some of the biggest and best design companies across the world. And now she wants to share what she’s learnt.

You can expect expert tips, learnings, and honest reflections on what the design industry is like today.
